節點文獻
王夫之《詩經》學研究



                    分頁CAJ下載
                

                        分章PDF下載
                    

                    整本CAJ下載
                

              整本PDF下載
            

                    在線閱讀
                

                不支持迅雷等下載工具。如閱讀文獻顯示異常，請下載並安裝新版CAJ閱讀器。



部分文獻由於文件較大，PDF全文下載時容易出現504錯誤，建議您優先選擇CAJ下載或PDF分章下載。

        【作者】
          納秀艷；
          

      【導師】
      董家平；
      

      【作者基本信息】
      陜西師範大學，
      中國古代文學，
      2014，
      博士
      
      【摘要】 王夫之是明末清初的一位思想家。他治《詩經》,博採眾長,卻不墨守陳規,勇於打破傳統經學研究的模式,獨立思考,見解深刻。他的《詩經》學在研究方法、詩學觀、美學觀等方面均有建樹。尤其是他於《詩經》研究中所闡發的思想,在《詩經》學史、乃至思想史上具有獨特的價值。他對清代《詩經》學的振興以及新學風的開創,具有篳路藍縷之功。目前,學界對於王夫之《詩經》學的研究,雖然取得了一定的成就,但是尚有不足。本文力圖對王夫之《詩經》學展開較全面的探討,嘗試對王夫之《詩經》學所蘊含的詩學觀、美學觀、方法論以及思想內涵,進行較深入的研究,發掘其《詩經》學在學術思想方面的重要價值,以期對王夫之《詩經》學研究領域的拓展,以盡綿薄之力。本文除緒論外,由六章構成,主要內容簡括如下：第一章介紹王夫之《詩經》學產生的文化背景。其一,豐富的《詩經》學成果。《詩經》學自先秦誕生以來,綿延數千年,成就卓越。王夫之汲取《詩經》學的養分,融入時代精神和個性特質,形成了內涵豐富、思想鮮明的《詩經》學特色。其二,易代之際的社會環境和文化思潮。明代自中期以來,政治腐敗,社會風氣衰退,士風不振,加之心學末流的影響,學術界出現虛浮現象,王夫之以經典研究為陣地,以求真務實的治學精神,糾正不良之風。滿清貴族為了鞏固統治地位,實施了一系列壓制漢民族的政策,激起了強烈的反抗情緒,清初嚴酷的文化氛圍,是王夫之《詩經》學極富批判性和思想性的原因之一。第二章探討王夫之《詩經》學的宗旨。王夫之於《詩經》研究,以“六經責我開生面”為宗旨,立足經典,探究《詩經》的文學特色,闡發深刻的思想,於《詩經》研究多有開創性意義。本章從精神實質、文化淵源及其《詩經》學的創新等方面,論述其《詩經》學的宗旨。第三章總結歸納王夫之研究《詩經》的基本方法。王夫之以不主常故為學術旨趣,在別開生面的學術研究中,能夠融通文史,探索了一些有益的治學方法,主要有專題研究式、科學歸納、以詩解《詩》等。這些方法的運用,使他的《詩經》學獨具特色,且成就卓越。對王夫之《詩經》學基本方法的探究,不僅有益於《詩經》研究,也有益於其他學科的研究。第四章闡述王夫之《詩經》學的詩學觀。主要對“詩際幽明”與“詩以道情”兩大詩學觀展開論述。“詩際幽明”是王夫之基於《詩經》祭祀詩歌的研究,提煉出的詩學觀,即“詩者,幽明之際也”,在這一詩學觀的指導下,他對《詩經》的祭歌進行深入研究,揭櫫《詩經》迥異的詩歌特色,展示《詩經》獨特的魅力。“詩以道情”是王夫之詮釋《詩經》抒情性的詩論,他結合文本,從多層面論述情感在詩歌中的地位和對詩人達情的要求。第五章論述王夫之《詩經》學的美學思想。主要對“詩樂合一”和“興觀群怨”兩大美學觀展開論述。王夫之在研究中,提出了以律度為本的美學觀,並對“詩樂合一”予以全新的闡釋,展示《詩經》獨具風貌的音樂美。“興觀群怨”是一個古老的美學命題,王夫之基於橫向與縱向的再討論,認為“興觀群怨”是表現人類情感的基本方式,也是四種情感類型,這是對傳統闡釋的新突破。第六章探討王夫之《詩經》學所表現出的生命情懷。立足於《詩廣傳》,剖析蘊涵於其中的憂懷家國的情感指向、重視人格的精神取向、重建秩序的美政理想等,充分論述王夫之在《詩經》研究中,寄予的情感訴求。這王夫之《詩經》學最富魅力之處,也是與眾不同之處。更多還原
      【Abstract】 Wang Fuzhi was a thinker in late Ming and early Qing dynasties. His study of the Book of Songs is based on others’ strong points but not cling to tradition. He made valuable contribution in research method, the view of poetics and the thought of aesthetics.Especially, his thought of the Book of Songs has an unique value in the history of the study of the Book of Songs even in intellectual history. His study revitalized the study of Book of Songs and promoted the study in Qing Dynasty.Currently, the academic members do a lot of research in Wang Fuzhi’s poetics and aesthetics. However, we also found that many places still inadequate. This paper tries to study Wang Fuzhi’s view of poetics, the thought of aesthetics, methodology and ideological connotation. What’s more, it is important to widen the research of Wang Fuzhi and to find the value on academic idea. Besides exordium, this paper consists of six chapters. Details are as follows:Chapter One is about the cultural background of Wang’s study of the Book of Songs. There are two critical influences on his study. Firstly, Wang made abundant achievements in this field. The study of Book of Songs was born in Pre-Qin period. It got excellent achievements through thousands of years. He learned widely from others’ strong points and formed his own style. Second is the harsh cultural atmosphere in early Qing Dynasty. Since the middle of Ming dynasty, under the affect of political orruption and moral decline, as well as Wang Yangming’s thoughts, academic circles was caught in superficial sentiment. Luckily, Wang Fuzhi, equipped with practical spirit of scholarship and study on classical works, changed the unhealthy social climate. Manchu Nobility who did mental and physical damage to Han Nationality implemented a serious policy in order to establish dominance. These actions aroused strong resistance which enforced this emotion to the loyalists of Ming Dynasty. All of these are the roots of Wang Fuzhi’s study why are full of criticalness and vitality. Chapter Two is about the purpose of Wang Fuzhi’s study. He aimed to "start a new phenomenon for Confucian". His main idea is to connect the classical research with the real life. The idea can meet the need that all learnings are to solve problems in life. Chapter Three sums up the basic approach of Wang’s research. Not only Wang Fuzhi can get resources from the research of previous generation, but also he has his independent thought. He put forward some useful methods on his research, such as comprehensive research, monographic study and explaining the Book of Songs with poetry. According to these methods, he divided his research into different classes in unity. These research methods not only make contributions to the research of Book of Songs, but also other subjects.Chapter Four is about to state Wang Fuzhi’s poetics opinion. This chapter discusses "the poetry is from the inside" and "the poetry is expressing the feelings". The former opinion sums up the trait theory of sacrificial songs in Greater Odes of the Kingdom and Odes of the Temple and the Alter. His opinion can uncover the magic of the sacrificial songs. The latter opinion reflects his attention on lyric poetry qualities. However, he emphasizes the poet should express emotions in moderation.Chapter Five is about to discuss Wang’s aesthetic thoughts in the study of the Book of Songs. It analyzes the thoughts of "combining poetry and music" and Confucius’s view of "Xing" poetry theory. Music is one of the basic traits in the Book of Songs. With the aesthetic thoughts that come from being music-centered, Wang Fuzhi shows the aesthetical traits of poetry that music and emotion should maintain consistency. Confucius’s view of "Xing" poetry theory is an old proposition. Based on the theory which Wang interprets in portrait way and landscape way, he declares that "Xing" poetry theory are four kinds human emotions. Obviously, this is a break from the traditional interpretation.Chapter Six discusses Wang Fuzhi’s vitality of the study of Book of Songs. This chapter mainly discusses his work——"Shi Guangzhuan", and the sense of crisis, emotions, spirit, complex, and vitality in it. What’s more, in this chapter, the writer shows the emotions of Wang Fuzhi when he studied in the Book of the Songs. This emotion is charming, moving, and distinctive in "Shi Guangzhuan" and also distinguished his from other researchers.更多還原

    【關鍵詞】 王夫之；
      《詩經》學；
      詩學觀；
      美學思想；
      生命；
      
    【Key words】 Wang Fuzhi；
      the study of the Book of Songs；
      the view of poetics；
      the thought of aesthetics；
      vitality；
      






